episodes.title: Burning Desire: The Fellowship is a Cult w/ Rowland
episodes.description: In today's Burning Desire, Rowland joins us to discuss how the fellowship Alcoholics Anonymous is a cult. APGTY is a weekly podcast with recovered members of Alcoholics Anonymous discussing the 12 Steps, sobriety, the fellowship and more. Drop us a line at: podcastgreaterthanyourself@gmail.com or on Instagram APGTY or Doctor Silkworth
